data.description: A must see 2-story in Fox Ridge showcasing 5bd and 3.5 bath!!! New Roof. Primary bedroom on the main floor including vaulted ceiling, large walk-in closet, walk in shower and double vanity. Open floor plan perfect for entertaining featuring a large front room with bay windows. There is also a Large family room with high ceilings and gas fireplace. Overlooking the family room is a spacious loft upstairs. All bedrooms are spacious with large closets and two of the bedrooms share a Jack and Jill. House features multiple storage closets throughout and two pantry closets. Come see this charming Home!
